e":"2018-05-28T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"唔好假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，唔娶窮女人嘅原因唔喺怕分家產，喺根本日常生活相處都有困難。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，平時為左陪佢，一齊食大家樂大快活吉吉家其實無問題。<br />\n<br />\n問題喺你會就佢，無奶油要你屋企人就埋佢，講緊平常食一餐，是旦叫姐姐買個餸，材料費都夠平時食大家樂一個月，可能喺佢世界入面，佢覺得好又一餐，唔好又一餐，何必食咁貴，但喺屋企人世界入面，喂大佬，我真喺唔覺得貴喎，食餐飯你都想有意見？<br />\n<br />\n而且兩邊生活態度同待人接物根本唔會相同，我唔喺話踩緊邊個，之但喺你將有錢人嘅世界觀放落相對窮嘅人身上喺一個災難，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n為對方又好，自己又好，早分好過，唔好勉強大家，佢無左你會更幸福。"},{"pid":"ac8e12d28edfcff32f32703ec8d93a19b0b2f491","tid":681004,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"港女係垃圾都唔係第一日既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c01439812ad909dd6dc01dfbac4987ce7a020b","tid":681004,"uid":91272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"男人都係咁點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申成日去日本旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd4cb447d203a71975421fdbb409284b3b5a2fc","tid":681004,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"嫁左有錢人<br />\n身家即刻多過你儲二百年錢啦"},{"pid":"79a299bbd5f4ac3ae0573a177b096d0627cccfd2","tid":681004,"uid":7905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"條女係咁好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6778f303954cec0c0328ca0ac4b49f57acf51ca1","tid":681004,"uid":53396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"亦都咁講<br />\n唔問返你攞巳經都係有價值呢條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd128dfcfd7373800a010d56b24c8f5308cf0aa4","tid":681004,"uid":180348,"like":2,"di